Pacific Islander
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a person from the Pacific Islands, especially those with strong New Zealand constitutional connections; early South Sea Islander now (in NZ) ISLANDER 2 q.v.
Origin:[none]
